text: Las Huacas is a corregimiento in Natá District, Coclé Province, Panama. It has a land area of and had a population of 1,585 as of 2010, giving it a population density of . Its population as of 1990 was 1,364; its population as of 2000 was 1,417. ==References== Category:Corregimientos of Coclé Province
